Location & Currency

Clean beauty should be readily accessible to all, that's why our award winning makeup and skincare continues to be available at affordable drug store prices. Always vegan, our professional quality cosmetics are filled to the brim with cruelty-free goodness, and never tested on animals garnering the Leaping Bunny! stamp of approval. In efforts to reduce our environmental impact, e.l.f. Cosmetics launched Project Unicorn, a commitment to stripping down cluttered packaging for more sustainable options. Since 2019, e.l.f. has eliminated over one million pounds of excess packaging waste.
